[
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 52.3,
    "text": "Hey, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.3,
    "endTime": 53.4,
    "text": "Yes, Patrick?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.5,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "Do you know how to swim?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.1,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.5,
    "endTime": 57.5,
    "text": "Me, either."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.7,
    "endTime": 60.5,
    "text": "Hmm, I wonder why we're not sinking to the bottom of Goo Lagoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.6,
    "endTime": 63.7,
    "text": "Patrick, you're floating!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.9,
    "endTime": 65.6,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.2,
    "endTime": 68.10000000000001,
    "text": "Hey, you're floating, too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.6,
    "endTime": 69.6,
    "text": "What happened?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.7,
    "endTime": 71.7,
    "text": "These weird bubbles saved us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.8,
    "endTime": 74.39999999999999,
    "text": "It's all purple and sticky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.5,
    "endTime": 76.1,
    "text": "And it's really stretchy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 79.10000000000001,
    "text": "It's some kind of goo bobble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.8,
    "endTime": 82.39999999999999,
    "text": "Well, the smell makes my nose tickle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 89.7,
    "text": "Hey, it bounces!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.3,
    "endTime": 104.3,
    "text": "Sorry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.3,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "Chum! Get your red hot chum here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.1,
    "endTime": 128.29999999999998,
    "text": "What's the deal?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.8,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "According to my algorithm, beachgoers should be famished and looking for a treat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.1,
    "endTime": 135.7,
    "text": "A treat like chum!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.8,
    "endTime": 136.8,
    "text": "Hello?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.2,
    "endTime": 139.29999999999998,
    "text": "It's perfectly edible, people!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.2,
    "endTime": 144.7,
    "text": "Oh, come on, man; this is my livelihood!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.3,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "Ah! A beautiful day, beachside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.1,
    "endTime": 150.6,
    "text": "I couldn't think of a thing that could ruin this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.7,
    "endTime": 152.39999999999998,
    "text": "I could think of a few."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.2,
    "endTime": 160.2,
    "text": "Hey, you're blocking my light."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.1,
    "endTime": 166.79999999999998,
    "text": "SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.8,
    "endTime": 173.0,
    "text": "Ah, sweet karma."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.1,
    "endTime": 176.2,
    "text": "It can come from the most boneheaded of places."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.6,
    "endTime": 181.2,
    "text": "Wait a second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.3,
    "endTime": 183.60000000000002,
    "text": "What are those bouncing blobs of goo?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.6,
    "endTime": 186.4,
    "text": "I don't know and I don't care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.7,
    "endTime": 191.89999999999998,
    "text": "Hold it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.7,
    "endTime": 197.7,
    "text": "What I want to know is why you two have ruined my attempts at having an even tan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.8,
    "endTime": 201.4,
    "text": "Oh, sorry, Squidward, we're riding on these cool goo bubbles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.5,
    "endTime": 203.6,
    "text": "They're floating out of Goo Lagoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.8,
    "endTime": 217.8,
    "text": "Stop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.9,
    "endTime": 220.20000000000002,
    "text": "Those bubbles are dangerous!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.3,
    "endTime": 221.8,
    "text": "Dangerous?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.9,
    "endTime": 223.5,
    "text": "Fascinating; tell us more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.6,
    "endTime": 226.2,
    "text": "Yeah, but with visual aids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.3,
    "endTime": 228.3,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.4,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "My scientific investigation has revealed that deep beneath the lagoon floor is a volcanic pocket of super goo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.1,
    "endTime": 243.29999999999998,
    "text": "A crack has formed, releasing bubbles with the goo to the surface, which are toxic and very unstable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.7,
    "endTime": 249.7,
    "text": "At any moment, it could lose its integrity and... boom! It'll explode!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 251.9,
    "text": "That rodent's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.0,
    "endTime": 255.7,
    "text": "A giant goo bubble could really level the playing field."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.8,
    "endTime": 261.2,
    "text": "If someone were able to control its power, they'd control all of Bikini Bottom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.6,
    "endTime": 264.3,
    "text": "And I'm gonna be that someone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.8,
    "endTime": 286.0,
    "text": "It's so gooey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.3,
    "endTime": 291.0,
    "text": "I can fit it in my mouth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.5,
    "endTime": 294.8,
    "text": "You idiots!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.9,
    "endTime": 296.29999999999995,
    "text": "That goo is dangerous!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.4,
    "endTime": 298.09999999999997,
    "text": "Weren't you two morons listening?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.4,
    "endTime": 301.59999999999997,
    "text": "No, not really; I drifted off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.7,
    "endTime": 303.8,
    "text": "But just look at all the cool stuff it can do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.2,
    "endTime": 308.0,
    "text": "You can make a hat or a beard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.1,
    "endTime": 310.3,
    "text": "Or an awesome toupee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.7,
    "endTime": 313.5,
    "text": "Toupee? You mean hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.7,
    "endTime": 316.59999999999997,
    "text": "How do I look?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.7,
    "endTime": 319.3,
    "text": "What is wrong with you people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.4,
    "endTime": 322.0,
    "text": "That goo can destroy everything!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.1,
    "endTime": 323.6,
    "text": "Seems safe to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.7,
    "endTime": 328.5,
    "text": "That's what they said about microwave ovens, dry cleaning, and corn dogs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.8,
    "endTime": 330.25,
    "text": "See you later, Sandy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.35,
    "endTime": 333.8,
    "text": "Yeah. These goo bubbles won't bounce themselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.6,
    "endTime": 339.0,
    "text": "You have been warned."
  }
]